      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CHAOTIC BOY (1) held his own to the line last start and filled a minor placing, beaten only a nose (16.99) behind Zinfandel Emma at this track. The form from his last run is stacking up nicely. Key chance in this line up. TATAMAGOUCHE (2) jumped from a squeeze box but quickly into stride and led until late to place second and beaten 3 lengths (20.04) at Angle Park in a Maiden over 342m. Nicely placed to grab a well-deserved win. VAPOUR GLOW (4) improved her time on first attempt here at the trip with a 2 length third in 17.14 latest. Strong run and expected to feature again. ADA BLAZE (6) has not raced here but still warrants respect.",
